Practical: 13: Write a program that can convert temperature from Centigrade to Fahrenheit

Program:
10    CLS
20     INPUT “ Temperature in Centigrade :=”; C
30     F = 9/5* C+32
40     PRINT “Temperature in Fahrenheit =”; F
50     END
Algorithm

Step 1  START
Step 2  INPUT      C
Step 3  COMPUTE    F = 9/5* C+32
Step 4  PRINT        F
Step 5  END
